# Troubleshooting (Maintainers)

When debugging SDK or integration failures, or editing troubleshooting docs, follow this workflow and check common causes.

Follow [docs/rules-of-engagement/troubleshooting.md](docs/rules-of-engagement/troubleshooting.md): **workflow** (Document → Research → Investigate → Resolve), **path namespace vs body UUID**, **List ServerError** ("Spec not full"), **list skips** (endorctl api list -r &lt;Resource&gt; --traverse; see troubleshooting.md), **list partial/mask**. Use endorctl to validate (e.g. `endorctl api list -r <Resource> --traverse -n <ns>`).

